Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.31,0:13:22.48,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}mado kara mieru awai hikari ga
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.48,0:13:29.37,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}yasashiku hoho wo terashiteiru
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.37,0:13:34.58,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}dokoka de kimi mo miteiru no kana
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.58,0:13:43.26,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}kono sora no shita tsunagatteru
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.74,0:14:12.03,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}sawameku konoha midori no nioi
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.03,0:14:18.83,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}machi no mannaka hitorikiri de
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.83,0:14:24.13,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}meguru kisetsu wo kanjitetan da
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.13,0:14:29.30,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}kawaribae no nai hibi
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.05,0:14:36.10,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}hiroi sekai ni nagedasareta you de
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.10,0:14:42.06,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}omowazu shita wo muita toki
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.06,0:14:48.11,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}chiisa na inochi no koe wo kiita yo
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.11,0:14:59.50,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}hora hitori ja nai kara daijoubu
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.33,0:15:07.67,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}kitto me wo tojitetara
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.67,0:15:15.56,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}kizukenai koto ga takusan arun da
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.56,0:15:24.15,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}kowagaranaide sukoshi de ii kara
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.15,0:15:32.49,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}mada dokenai yuuki{?} de fumidashite
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.67,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}nanigenai koto kurikaesu hibi de
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.67,0:15:55.93,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}kawasu kotoba wa kimi mo nakute
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.35,0:16:01.64,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}dakedo tashika ni oshiete kureta
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.64,0:16:07.52,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}tsunagatteiru koto wo
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.52,0:16:13.61,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}futto shita toki ni kokoro de kanjita yo
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.61,0:16:19.58,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}yosou mo tsukanai mirai wa
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.58,0:16:25.38,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}totsuzen otozureru maebure mo naku
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.80,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}mou hitori ja nain da
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.80,0:16:36.18,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}kitto kokoro no oku de
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.18,0:16:44.06,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}mebuite yuku kono atataka na kimochi
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.06,0:16:52.61,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}aseranakute mo ii hitotsu hitotsu zutsu
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.61,0:17:01.91,Insert Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}sodatete yukou tomo ni aru kiseki wo
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.31,0:13:22.48,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Bledé světlo oknem prochází,
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.48,0:13:29.37,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}jemně pohladí mě po tváři.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.37,0:13:34.58,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Jestlipak svítí i na tebe, ať už jsi kdekoliv...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.58,0:13:43.26,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Spojuje nás klenba nebeská.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.74,0:14:12.03,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Cítím vůni života, vždy když zašelestí listí.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.03,0:14:18.83,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}A i tam v centru města,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.83,0:14:24.13,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}mám pocit, jako bych zažila zázrak.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.13,0:14:29.30,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Nic mi ty dny nemůže nahradit,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.05,0:14:36.10,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}když vlny života tříští se nade mnou.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.10,0:14:42.06,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}Ani jsem si neuvědomila, že jsem chodila se sklopenýma očima.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.06,0:14:48.11,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}A pak jsem uslyšela slabý hlas života, jak říká:
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.11,0:14:59.50,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)\blur0.6}“Neboj se, ty nejsi sám.”
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.33,0:15:07.67,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Jsem si jistá, že existuje spousta věcí,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.67,0:15:15.56,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}které se zavřenýma očima nevnímáme.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.56,0:15:24.15,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Neboj se, zůstaň se mnou o něco déle,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.15,0:15:32.49,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}dokud nesebereme odvahu jít dál.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.29,0:15:49.67,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Dny ubíhají jeden za druhým,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.67,0:15:55.93,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}a nám oběma došla slova.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.35,0:16:01.64,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Přesto však cítím s jistotou,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.64,0:16:07.52,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}že nás něco spojuje.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.52,0:16:13.61,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Jednou se mému srdci jistě uleví.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.61,0:16:19.58,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Možná netušíme, co nám chystá budoucnost,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.58,0:16:25.38,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}ale víme jistě, že pro nás má spoustu překvapení.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.80,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Víme, že nejsme sami.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.80,0:16:36.18,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Tento hřejivý pocit v mém srdci
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.18,0:16:44.06,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}jistě tiše pokvete dál.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.06,0:16:52.61,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}Nemusíme nikam pospíchat, takže jeden po druhém
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.61,0:17:01.91,Insert English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.6}vytvořme spolu tyto zázraky.
